cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.ET, cs.SE, cs.AR 

The paper focuses on the security and trustworthiness of ICs, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses CAD and manufacturing flows, which are related to computer-aided design (cs.DC) and electronic design automation (cs.ET). The paper also touches upon software engineering (cs.SE) in terms of developing a practical threat model and conducting experiments. Finally, the paper proposes a new approach to 3D integration, which falls under the category of computer architecture (cs.AR).
